---
---

<section class="sect" id="problem">
  <div class="wrap">

    <p class="sect-eyebrow" data-reveal>The Problem</p>
    <h2 class="sect-heading" data-reveal>Bundle install takes<br />forever. Every time.</h2>
    <p class="sect-body" data-reveal>
      Ruby developers waste hours waiting for <code>bundle install</code>.<br />
      Docker builds fail because of gem path issues. CI pipelines crawl.
    </p>

    <div class="symptoms" data-stagger>
      <div class="symptom">
        <p class="symptom-name">5-30 min installs</p>
        <p class="symptom-desc">Complex Gemfiles with native extensions take forever. Parallel downloads are an afterthought.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="symptom">
        <p class="symptom-name">Docker gem issues</p>
        <p class="symptom-desc">"gem not found" errors in containers. Bundler path mismatches between dev and prod.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="symptom">
        <p class="symptom-name">500ms just to start</p>
        <p class="symptom-desc">Ruby interpreter startup + Bundler loading = half second gone before any work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="symptom">
        <p class="symptom-name">Slow CI/CD</p>
        <p class="symptom-desc">Gem installation is the bottleneck. Every commit waits for bundler to finish.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sect {
    padding: var(--sp-24) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sect-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .sect-heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-3xl));
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .sect-body {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-12);
  }

  .symptoms {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-12);
  }

  .symptom {
    padding: var(--sp-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .symptom:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
  .symptom:nth-child(3), .symptom:nth-child(4) { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .symptom-name {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .symptom-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .symptoms { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .symptom { border-right: none; }
  }
</style>
